com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.realtime

Interface SubscriptionListener


  • public interface SubscriptionListener
    A SubscriptionListener receives real time notifications to which it was subscribed to.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onError(String channel, Throwable error)
      If the CepConnector receives an error then it will pass it on to all it's listeners by calling this method.
      void onNotification(String channel, Notification notification)
      This method will be called by the CepConnector for each matching notification that it receives.

    • Method Detail

      • onNotification

        void onNotification(String channel,
                    Notification notification)
        This method will be called by the CepConnector for each matching notification that it receives.
        Parameters:
        channel - the channel that the listener subscribed to.
        notification - the Notification that contains all the matching response lines.

      • onError

        void onError(String channel,
             Throwable error)
        If the CepConnector receives an error then it will pass it on to all it's listeners by calling this method.
        Parameters:
        channel - name of the channel where the error happened.
        error - the Throwable that contains the error.
